My_Review: A bit snacky. I believed in most of the core ideas in the book before reading itself, so confirmed some of my biases. The author believes in anti-fragility, but still prescribes heave handed. Also, sometimes the tone is too blamy. Could have been shorter. Its fun to see some of these things in Indian context.
